      "span_text": "They were then washed thrice with phosphate-buffered solution, blocked with 0.5% bovine serum albumin for 1 h at 37 1C and incubated overnight at 4 1C with antibodies directed toward typical neuronal markers as described earlier.  In the negative control experiments, the primary antibody was omitted."
